abstract: New York City police announce arrest of Jerry Maisonett, second suspect in killing of Rosie Sanchez and Anderson Nunez in Brooklyn; other suspect is Sanchez's daughter Destiny Garcia.
lead_paragraph: Jerry Maisonett was charged with second-degree murder and criminal possession of a weapon in connection with the deaths of Rosie Sanchez and Anderson Nunez, the police said.

headline.main: 2nd Suspect Arrested in Killing of Brooklyn Couple
